        "2485": {
          "vnum": 2485,
          "name": "A Twisting Underwater Tunnel",
          "description": "The tunnel bends slowly from northwest to east, and the light shifts gradually from green to orange. An odd feeling of closeness overwhelms you briefly, and you imagine the cavern as a bag and the tunnel as a hand within the bag grasping for you. Perhaps you should make your way out soon.",
