        "2487": {
          "vnum": 2487,
          "name": "Shallow Pool",
          "description": "You stand in a placid pool of cold water. A bright orange sky arcs above you, stretching across a long cavern extending far to the south. The floor of the cavern appears to be dirt, but is perhaps merely layer upon layer of guano deposited by the light brown, stork-like birds that stride about within the cavern. Looking down into the water, you spot an opening in the stone wall.",
