          "vnum": 2488,
          "name": "Beneath an Orange Sky",
          "description": "The dirty soil of the cavern floor slopes upward here from west to east, from a still pool of water to a plateau of higher ground. The cavern continues to the north and south as well, where you see more striders walking about.",
