        "2490": {
          "vnum": 2490,
          "name": "Beneath an Orange Sky",
          "description": "The brilliant orange sky bears down on your soul, transforming the merely unusual into the mundane. You trudge across the dirty floor of the cavern, dragging your feet and hunching your shoulders. The ground slopes down to the west, and you see a bright pool in the distance. The cavern also continues to the north and to the south, where a bend obscures your view.",
