        "2491": {
          "vnum": 2491,
          "name": "Narrow Passage between Caverns",
          "description": "This narrow passage leads from one large cavern into another, from northeast to southwest. Both caverns, as well as the passage itself, are marked by the magical orange light, and together they might be taken as a single cavern. From the passage, you can clearly see the odd stone shapes spread about the ground to your southwest. You have lost 72 experience.",
