        "2494": {
          "vnum": 2494,
          "name": "Beneath an Orange Sky",
          "description": "From this northern end of the cavern you watch as young striders approach the pool to the southwest, occasionally pulling forth a thin black snake, occasionally being pulled under by a thicker one. The orange skyline extends far to the south, and a short distance to the east, while rough stone walls rise to the north and west.",
