        "3064": {
          "vnum": 3064,
          "name": "Cavern of Strange Stones",
          "description": "Unlike those to the north, many of the striders in this section of the cavern of orange stand stoicly at their posts. Anxiously awaiting your approach, they sharpen their beaks on the stone forms as they watch you carefully from beady brown eyes. The cavern continues to the east and south.",
